sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as Client
  participant Api as ApiNode
  participant Cmd as KafkaCommands
  participant Worker as CommandWorker
  participant Store as EventStore
  participant Outbox as EventPublisher
  participant Proj as ProjectionWorker
  participant ReadDb as ReadModelDB

  Client->>Api: POST reserve(itemId,userId,idempotencyKey)
  Api->>Cmd: Produce ReserveCommand key=itemId
  Cmd->>Worker: Deliver command from partition
  Worker->>Store: Load current version and state
  Worker->>Store: Append ReservationCreated with expectedVersion
  Store-->>Worker: Commit success and new version
  Worker->>Outbox: Publish ReservationCreated
  Outbox->>Proj: Deliver domain event
  Proj->>ReadDb: Upsert reservation projection
  Api->>ReadDb: Read by idempotencyKey or reservationId
  ReadDb-->>Api: Current reservation state
  Api-->>Client: 200 with reservation payload
